data.enText: a situation in which two or more things are not the same size or are not treated the same, in a way that is unfair or causes problems

data.chText: 我们正努力纠正进出口的不平衡。
data.enText: Attempts are being made to redress (= put right) the imbalance between our import and export figures.

tr: a lack of balance or state of disequilibrium

value.def: If there is an imbalance in a situation, the things involved are not the same size, or are not the right size in proportion to each other.

example.ex: ...the imbalance between the two sides in this war.
example.tran: 这场战争中双方力量的悬殊

example.ex: ...an international strategy to reduce trade imbalances.
example.tran: 降低贸易逆差的国际战略
